  "title": "AB03 - Retail Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Retail Assistant (Cakes and Cupcakes Store)</strong><br />Gross Salary: $2000 - $2200 + AWS<br />Working Days: 5 days (11 hours shift) / 6 days (9 hours shift)<br />Working Location: Orchard / Bugis (Rotating)</p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Greet and assist customers in a friendly and professional manner.</li><li>Provide information about cupcake flavours, ingredients, and promotions.</li><li>Take and process customer orders accurately (in-store, takeaway, or online).</li><li>Handle payments, operate the cash register, and balance the till at the end of the shift.</li><li>Ensure cupcakes and display shelves are well-presented and stocked throughout the day.</li><li>Maintain cleanliness of the store, including the display area, tables, and counters.</li><li>Assist with packaging, labelling, and replenishing baked goods.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>With F&B working experience</li></ul><p><strong>If you are keen to apply, please send me your resume and job applied for on WhatsApp at 8093 8699 or email me at anabel.thesupreme@gmail.com (˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶)</strong></p><p>❄️Anabel Boon Xue Qi | Consultant Associate (R25159272) |📍The Supreme HR Advisory EA No: 14C7279</p>",
